Invocation Name: fortune mash
des:
Mansion, apartment, shack, or house ... find out what your future has in store! And who you will spend it with ...

Just give Alexa four names, and Fortune MASH will predict who you'll end up with, how many kids you'll have, what type of home you live in, and what vehicle you drive!* If you don't like the outcome, just try again to hear a different one. The possibilities are endless!

*More categories will be added with future updates. Leave us a review with a feature suggestion and maybe your idea will get added to the skill!
